{"product_id":"rhubarb-hair-mask-with-castor-oil-250-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11509\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/5-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11514\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/6-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11524\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/8-300x300.png\" alt=\"global green beauty awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11519\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/7-300x300.png\" alt=\"buduaar beauty award 2022\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927707627847,"sku":"","price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-250ml-9001472.png?v=1763665705","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/rhubarb-hair-mask-with-castor-oil-250-ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}